\id EPH 50EPHKENU.SFM Kenyang New Testament June 2009
\h Ɛfɛsɔs
\toc1 Ɛkáti Pɔ̌l ntá Nkwɔ Ɛfɛsɔs
\toc2 Nkwɔ Ɛfɛsɔs
\toc3 Ɛfɛs
\mt2 Ɛkáti Pɔ̌l ntá
\mt1 Nkwɔ Ɛfɛsɔs
\c 1
\s1 Ɛkáti ɛnɛ Pɔ̌l asɨ́ŋɨ́ ntá bǒnkwɔ abhɛn Ɛ́fɛsɔs
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔ̌l, mǔntó Yesu Kristo bɛkoŋo nkaysi Mandɛm, kɛ nchí sɨŋ ɛkáti ɛnɛ.
\p Nchí sɨŋ ntá yɛka bo Mandɛm abhɛn bǎbhʉ̀rɛ bariɛp ndǔ Mandɛm áchɛ́mɛ́ bhe nɛ Yesu Kristo.
\v 2 Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ nɛ Acha yɛsɛ Yesu Kristo mántɔ́ŋ be bɛrɨ̌ndu, mánchyɛ be kpák.
\s1 Ɛnyu Mandɛm áyɛ̀t bɛsɛ ndǔ sɛ́bhárɛ́mʉɛt nɛ Yesu
\p 
\v 3 Sɛ́mbɨ́tí Mandɛm Mmu achi Chi Yesu Kristo Acha ywɛsɛ. Yi achyɛ́ bhɛsɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ áfɔ́k anɛ́ áfù amfay ndǔ nɛbhʉɛt anɛ yi achi Mfɔ arɛ́, mbɔnyunɛ ábhat bhɛsɛ nɛ Kristo.
\v 4 Mandɛm ápɛ́rɛ́ ghoko mmɨk, anáŋ ayap nyaka bhɛsɛ ndu áchɛ́mɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Kristo, bɛ sɛ́mbák nyáŋá, kɛbhɔ́ŋ bɛkwɛ́nɛ́ bɛsí bhi.
\v 5 Ndu ákɔ́ŋ bhɛsɛ, anáŋ atɨ nyaka bɛ sɛ́mfʉ́ɛ́t ntá Yesu Kristo sɛmbak bɔ̌bhi. Akʉ nɔ bɛkoŋo ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ yi átɨ́ nyaka bɛkʉ,
\v 6 bɛ sɛ́mbɨ́tí yi ɛ̌ti bɛyǎ bɛrɨ̌ndu ɛbhɛn yi átɔ́ŋɔ́ bhɛsɛ ndɛ́ndɛm, ndu ábhárɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Mɔ́ywi mmu yi akɔŋ tontó.
\v 7 Mandɛm aku bhɛsɛ nɛ manoŋ Kristo afɛ́rɛ́ ndǔ kɛsɛm ndu ábhárɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Kristo. Nɛ afóŋórí bhɛsɛ ndǔ sɛ́pú bhʉɛrɛ bɛbhé. Akʉ nɔ bɛkoŋo ɛnyǔ yi átɔ́ŋ bhɛsɛ bɛyǎ bɛrɨ̌ndu
\v 8 ɛbhɛn yi áre tɔŋ bhɛsɛ, akʉ nkwɔ bɛ sɛ́mbɔ́ŋ nɛrɨŋɨ́ndak nɛnkɛm nɛ nɛjwǐmɛm nɛnkɛm.
\v 9 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ yi átɨ́ nyaka bɛkʉ ɛnɛ́ sɛ́bhɨ́kɨ́re rɨŋɨ nyaka, atɨ̌ bɛkʉ yɔ bɛfʉɛt ndu mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn Kristo ákʉ́.
\v 10 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛyɔ nɔ Mandɛm atɨ bɛkʉ ɛchi nyaka bɛ mpok ánáŋ ánkwáy, yi ǎchɛm mɛnyɨŋ mɛnkɛm, ɛbhɛn amfay nɛ ɛbhɛn fá amɨk, amfyɛ́ amɔ Kristo.
\v 11 Mandɛm ǎkʉ̀ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ mbɔ ɛnyǔ yi átɨ́ bɛkʉ. Ayap bhɛsɛ tɛntɛp ndu ákɔ́ŋ nyaka bɛkʉ nɔ, bɛ́ sɛ́mbák bɔ̌bhi ndǔ yi ábhárɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Kristo mbɔnyunɛ yi ákʉ̀ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn yi átɨ́ nyaka bɛkʉ bɛkoŋo mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn yi áyàŋ bɛkʉ.
\v 12 Bɛsɛ́ bho sɛ́yámbɨ bɛbhaka ntɨ nɛ Kristo sɛbhɔŋ bɛkʉ bo mámbɨ́tɨ́ yi ɛ̌ti kɛnɛ́m ɛki.
\v 13 Ɛchi ɛnyumɔt nɛ bhe nkwɔ. Mǎnáŋ bǎghok ɛyɔŋ ɛnɛ ɛchi tɛtɛp, nɛ chí Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ bɛ Mandɛm ǎpɛmɛ chɔŋ bhe, nɛ mǎnókó Kristo. Mpok anɛ mǎnókó, Mandɛm achyɛ bhe Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ mbɔ sɛbhaŋ ndu bɛtɔŋ bɛ bǎchi bǒbhi nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyu yi afyɛ́ nyaka bariɛp bɛ ǎkʉ.
\v 14 Achyɛ́ bhɛsɛ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ mmu yi áchyɛ̀ bɔ̌bhi. Ɛ̌ti yɔ, sɛ́rɨŋɨ bɛ Mandɛm ǎfɛrɛ chɔŋ bɛsɛ mankɛm bo sɛ́chí bɔ̌bhi ndǔ kɛsɛm. Ɛnɛ ɛ́kʉ́ bo báre bɨti Mandɛm ndǔ bɛtaŋ ɛbhi bɛyǎ bɛcha.
\s1 Pɔ̌l ǎnɨ̀kmʉɛt ɛ̌ti bǒnkwɔ abhɛn Ɛ́fɛsɔs
\p 
\v 15 Tɛ mpok anɛ njámbɨ ngoko bɛ bǎsɨ́kɨ́ ntɨ nɛ Yesu Acha nɛ bɛ́ bǎkɔŋ bo Mandɛm mankɛm,
\v 16 mbɨ́kɨ́ rɔ bɛkaka Mandɛm ɛ̌ti yɛka ndǔ mpok anɛ mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt.
\v 17 Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt ntá Mandɛm mmu ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛtaŋ mɛnkɛm. Achi Mandɛm Yesu Kristo Acha ywɛsɛ. Achi nkwɔ Ɛtayi. Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ yi anchyɛ bhe Ɛfóŋó yi mmu ákʉ̀ mǎndɨŋɨ Mandɛm mǎndɔk nɔkɔ chi ambɨ.
\v 18 Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ yi ánɛ́nɛ́ batɨ̌ yɛka sayri ɛnyu ɛnɛ́ bǎrɨŋɨ manɛ́m mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bǎbháká ntɨ arɛ bɛ chɔŋ yi ankʉ ntá bo abhɛn yi ábhɨ́ŋɨ́. Nchí yaŋ bɛ mǎndɨŋɨ bɛyǎ áfɔ́k anɛ yi afyɛ́ bariɛp ndu bɛkʉ manɛ́m mɛnyɨŋ ntá bo abhɛn bachi abhi.
\v 19 Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ mǎndɨŋɨ ɛnyǔ bɛtaŋ ɛbhi bɛyǎ ɛnyǔ ɛnɛ́ sɛpu kway bɛyɛnti bhɔ. Bɛyǎ ndu bɛkwak bhɛsɛ bho sɛ́nókó yi. Bɛtaŋ ɛbhi bhɔ bɛyǎ tontó.
\v 20 Nɛ nkúbhɛ́ bɛtaŋ ɛbhɛn kɛ Mandɛm ákʉ́ nyaka Yesu ápɛ́rɛ́nsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m achɔkɔ ɛbhě awɔ́nɛm ywi awu amfay ndǔ nɛbhʉɛt anɛ Kristo achi arɛ mbɔ Mfɔ.
\v 21 Arɛ́, abhɔ́ŋ bɛtaŋ amfǎy bɔángɛl mankɛm nɛ bafɔ bhap, nɛ amfǎy yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ ɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛtaŋ awu amfay nɛ fá amɨk. Abhɔŋ bɛtaŋ amfǎy bafɔ mankɛm, abhɛn bakwǎŋwaŋ nɛ abhɛn bachi bɛfóŋó nkwɔ amfǎy bo abhɛn báchí ndǔ nɛŋɔkɔ́mɨk ɛnɛn mfay ɛnɛn nɛ́twɔ̀.
\v 22 Afyɛ́ mɛnyɨŋ mɛnkɛm amɔ́ yi bɛ ndǔ ákʉ́ yi mmu abhɔŋ bɛtaŋ amfay yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ, ámbák mǔnti ntá bǒnkwɔ.
\v 23 Nɛ bǒnkwɔ mankɛm báchí mmʉɛt Yesu. Amʉɛt bǒnkwɔ kɛ bághɔ bɛrɨ̌ Kristo mɛnkɛm nɛ mbák chi Kristo, amʉɛrɛ-yi kɛ bo bághɔ bɛrɨ Mandɛm.
\c 2
\s1 Mandɛm áchyɛ̀ nɛpɛ́m nɛkɔ ntá bo Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Ndǔ mpok anɛ afʉɛ́rɛ́ ansɛm, bǎchi nyaka mbɔ bawú bɛsí Mandɛm mbɔnyunɛ bǎpú bhʉɛrɛ nyaka bɛbhé Mandɛm ɛ̌ti bɛyǎ bɛbʉ́ ɛbhɛka.
\v 2 Mpok yɔ, bɛpɨŋ ɛbhɛka bɛbhak chi ɛbhɛn bǒ mmɨk nɛ mǎnkoŋo nɔkɔ chi mfɔ bɛfóŋó bɛbʉ́bɛbʉ anɛ, nɛ́nɛ, abhɔ̌ŋ bɛtaŋ ndǔ bɛpɨŋɨ́ bho. Mfɔ bɛfóŋó wu ǎkɛ̀m batɨ̌ bo abhɛn bátàŋti nɛ Mandɛm.
\v 3 Bɛsɛ mankɛm nkwɔ sɛ́kʉ̀ nyaka mbɔ bhɔ, sɛ́nkoŋo nɔkɔ chi bɛbɛ́ptí mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn mmʉɛt ɛyɛsɛ nɛ batɨ̌ yɛsɛ áŋwàka bɛ sɛnkʉ. Ndǔ ntee ayɛsɛ yɔ, Mandɛm abhɔ̌ŋ nyaka bɛchyɛ bhɛsɛ ntɛ́msí mbɔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu achak ndu ábé nyaka ntɨ tontó ɛ̌ti bɛbʉ́.
\v 4 Kɛ ntínso Mandɛm nɛya tontó. Atɔ́ŋ yɛ bhɛsɛ chi ɛkɔŋ ɛyi ɛnɛ ɛ́yá ɛ́chá.
\v 5 Nɛ yɛ̌ chi mpok anɛ sɛ́chí nyaka mbɔ bawú ɛ̌ti sɛpu bhʉɛrɛ bɛbhé Mandɛm, yí akʉ sɛ́bhak nɛpɛ́m chɛ́chɛm nɛ Kristo mmu ápɛ́rɛ́nsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m. Bɛkoŋo bɛrɨ̌ndu ɛbhi kɛ̌ yi ápɛ́mɛ́ bhé.
\v 6 Ndu Mandɛm ábhárɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Yesu Kristo, yí akʉ sɛ́pɛtnsɛm ndǔ nɛpɛ́m nɛ yi. Nɛ akʉ sɛ́chɔ́kɔ́ nɛ Kristo amfay ndǔ nɛbhʉɛt anɛ yi achi Mfɔ.
\v 7 Ákʉ́ bhɛsɛ bɛyǎ bɛrɨ ɛnyu yɔ bɛfʉɛt ndǔ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ Yesu Kristo ákʉ́ ndu bɛkwak bhɛsɛ bɛ sɛ́ntɔ́ŋ bo abhɛn mpok anɛ átwɔ̀ ansɛm ɛnyǔ bɛrɨ̌ndu ɛbhi bɛyǎ tontó ɛnyu ɛnɛ sɛ́pú kway bɛyɛnti bhɔ.
\v 8 Mandɛm ápɛ́mɛ́ bhe ɛ̌ti bɛrɨ̌ndu bhi nɛ ndǔ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ nɛka nɛ yi. Abhɨ́kɨ́ pɛmɛ bhe ɛ̌ti bɛrɨ́tí mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bǎkʉ̀, chi akap anɛ yi áchyɛ́ bhe ndɛ́ndɛm.
\v 9 Mandɛm abhɨ́kɨ́ pɛmɛ be bɛ bǎkʉ nyaka bɛrɨ́tí bɛtɨk. Yɛ̌ mmu ákɛ́ pá yɛ nnyu.
\v 10 Sɛ́chí yɛ chí awɔ́-bɛtɨk Mandɛm. Aghókó bhɛsɛ, abhat nɛ Yesu Kristo, bɛ́ sɛ́nkʉ́ nɔ́kɔ́ chí bɛrɨ́tí mɛnyɨŋ. Nɛ Mandɛm anáŋ átóŋtí nyaka bɛrɨ́tí mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ ábhʉ́rɛ́ ntá yɛsɛ, bɛ sɛ́nkʉ nɔkɔ bhɔ.
\s1 Yesu Kristo akʉ sɛrɔp chi mmu amɔt
\p 
\v 11 Bě bho bǎpú bo Israɛl, bǎkɛ ghɔkɔntɨk ɛnyǔ bǎchí nyaka ndǔ mpok anɛ áfʉɛ́rɛ́ ansɛm. Bo Israɛl básyɛp bho, nɛ ɛ̌ti yɔ bábhɨ̀ŋɨ mmʉɛt yap bɛ, “Bo abhɛn bǎsyɛphɛ bho nɛ bǎbhɨ̀ŋɨ bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl bɛ, bo abhɛn babhɨkɨ syɛp bhɔ.” \f + \fr 2:11 \ft “Bo abhɛn bábhɨ́kɨ́ syɛp bhɔ”: Nnyɛ́n ɛnɛn chi nnyɛ́n kɛyɔkɔ́ ndu bɛtɔŋ bɛ bo abhɛn babhɨkɨ syɛp bhɔ bapu pɛ́pɛ́p bɛsí Mandɛm.\f*
\v 12 Bǎkɛ́ ghɔkɔntɨk bɛ mpok ɛyɔ bǎbhɨkɨ bhɔŋ nyaka yɛ̌nyɨŋ bɛkʉ nɛ Kristo. Bě kɛbhɔŋ ɛnyɨŋ nɛ bǎbhak mankɔ ndu nkwɔ bo abhɛn Mandɛm áyábhɛ́ afyɛ́ bariɛp ɛ̌ti mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn yi áyàŋ bɛkʉ ntá yap, kɛ ɛyɔ ɛbhɨkɨ yɨŋɨ nyaka bhe. Bǎbhɨ́kɨ́ bhɔŋ nyaka yɛ̌nyɨŋ ɛnɛ́ bǎbhaka ntɨ arɛ́ mǎnòŋ nɔkɔ fá ndǔ mmɨkɨ nɛ, nɛ be kɛrɨŋɨ Mandɛm.
\v 13 Bǎsap nyaka nɛkɔ nɛ Mandɛm, kɛ nɛ́nɛ, Mandɛm abhat be nɛ Yesu Kristo, ákʉ mǎmbák kɛkwɔt nɛ yi bɛfʉɛt ndǔ manoŋ Kristo amɛn árɔ́ŋɔ́ amɨk.
\v 14 Kristo yímbɔŋ ákʉ́ bhɛsɛ́ bo Israɛl nɛ be bho bǎpu bo Israɛl bɛ sɛ́mbák kpák nɛ batɨ. Mpap achí nyaka nɛntɨ ɛnɛsɛ mbɔ nkók anɛ ákɔ́rɛ́ bhɛsɛ. Afɛ́rɛ́ mpap ayɔ mpok yi ágú, akʉ sɛ́rɔp chi mmu amɔt.
\v 15 Achɔ́ŋtí bɛtaŋ ɛbhɛn bɛbhé Moses mɛnkɛm. Mbɔk bɛbhé bɛbhak ɛ̌ti mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bo babhɔŋɔ bɛkʉ. Bɛchak bɛkóŋo bɛpɨŋɨ́tɔk. Akʉ́ ɛnyuyɔ bɛ bakwɔ́ bho apay andɔp chi nkwɔ amɔt, nɔ chi, nkwɔ bo bakɔ abhɛn Mandɛm ábhárɛ́ nɛ yi. Ɛnyu ɛyɔ kɛ̌ yi akʉ kpák ámbák nɛntɨ bo Israɛl nɛ abhɛn bapu bo Israɛl.
\v 16 Afɛ́rɛ́ mpap nɛntɨ bakwɔ́ bho bhɔ apay bɛfʉɛt ndǔ nɛwú ɛni ndǔ ɛkotákátí. Akʉ bɛ́ bakwɔ́ bho apay mándɔp chi nkwɔ amɔt, nɛ bɛ bo Israɛl nɛ abhɛn bapu bo Israɛl, mambak ɛrɨrɨ nɛ Mandɛm.
\v 17 Atwɔ́ yɛ aghati Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ árɛ̀m bɛ kpák achi nɛ bě bho bǎchi nyaka nɛkɔ nɛsiɛ nɛ abhɛn bachi kɛkwɔt.
\v 18 Chi bɛfʉɛt ntá Yesu Kristo kɛ Ɛfóŋó Mandɛm ákwàk bhɛsɛ nɛ be bɛ sɛ́mbɔ́ŋ mbi bɛrɔŋ ntá Ɛta.
\p 
\v 19 Bě bho bǎpu bo Israɛl bǎpɛt bǎpú yɛ mankɔ, nɛ bǎpú bo abhɛn báfú nɛkɔ nɛsiɛ. Bǎrɔp chí bǒ ɛtɔk mbɔ bo Mandɛm bachak, nɛ bǒ nnɛrɛkɛt Mandɛm anɛ áchí mbɔ ɛfo ɛ́mɔt.
\v 20 Bě nɛ bhɔ bǎchi bɛkpɔkɔ́ ntɔp ɛbhɛn básɔ́rɛ́ báté ɛkɛt ɛyɔ. Barɛmɛ́ kɛpɨ̌ntɨ nɛ bǒnto Yesu báchí nɛbhʉɛ́rɛ́kɛt ɛnɛn bághókó báté ɛkɛt ɛyɔ arɛ, nɛ Yesu Kristo yímbɔŋ achi ɛkwap ɛnɛ ɛ́kɛ̀m ɛkɛt.
\v 21 Yi akʉ bɛsɛ bho sɛchi maŋɔkɔ́kɛt nyáŋá nyáŋá sɛ́bhàt mmʉɛt nɛ batɨ sayri ɛnyu ɛnɛ ɛkɛrákap ɛ́té sɛnɛ nɛ ɛ́gò bɛbhak nyáŋá ndǔ ɛchi ntá Acha.
\v 22 Nɛ ndǔ Mandɛm áchɛ́mɛ́ bhe nɛ Kristo, yí ákʉ́ bǎbhàt mmʉɛt nɛ bǒnkwɔ bachak mankɛm bɛ be nɛ bhɔ mǎmbák ɛkɛt ɛnɛ Mandɛm áchɔ̀kɔ arɛ bɛfʉɛt ntá bɛtaŋ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ.
\c 3
\s1 Bɛtɨk ɛbhɛn Pɔ̌l ákʉ́ ntá bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔ̌l, mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt ntá Mandɛm ɛ̌ti yɛka bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl. Nchí mǔkɛnɔŋ mbɔnyunɛ nchí ghati bho Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ ɛ̌ti Yesu Kristo ndu bɛkwak bhe.
\v 2 Nkáysí bɛ mǎnaŋ bǎghok ɛ̌ti bɛtɨk ɛbhɛn Mandɛm áchyɛ́ mɛ ɛ̌ti bɛrɨ̌ndu ɛbhi bɛ nkʉ ndǔ bɛkwak bhe.
\v 3 Atɔ́ŋ mɛ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́chí nyaka bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́, ákú ndɨ́ŋɨ́ bhɔ, mbɔ ɛnyǔ nsɨ́ŋɨ́ mandú ngátí bhe ɛ̌ti mbɔk mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ.
\v 4 Mpok bǎpày ɛkáti ɛnɛ, chɔŋ mǎnkwáy bɛghɔ bɛ njwímɛm sayri ndǔ nkaysi Mandɛm anɛ achi nyaka bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́ ɛ̌ti Kristo.
\v 5 Ndǔ mkpáká bho anɛ ɛ́fʉɛ́rɛ́ ansɛm, Mandɛm abhɨ́kɨ́ kʉ bho mándɨŋɨ nkaysi yɔ, mbɔ ɛnyǔ yi ákʉ́ nɛ́nɛ bɛ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ ántɔ́ŋ yɔ ntá bǒnto nɛ barɛmɛ́ kɛpɨ̌ntɨ bhi, bɔ́ bho báchi nyáŋá ntá yi.
\v 6 Nkaysi bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́ yɔ achi bɛ bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl bábhɔ̀ŋ nkwɔ áfɔ́k anɛ bo Israɛl bábhɔ̀ŋ, bɛ bɔ bárɔp chi mmu amɔt nɛ bo Israɛl nɛ bɛ chɔŋ mámbɔŋ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn Mandɛm afyɛ́ bariɛp bɛ ǎkʉ ntá bɔ̌bhi ndǔ yi ábhárɛ́ bhɔ nɛ Kristo. Bɛfʉɛt ndǔ Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ ɛ̌ti Yesu Kristo kɛ bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ.
\p 
\v 7 Mandɛm atɔŋ mɛ bɛrɨ̌ndu, asɔt mɛ bɛ nkʉ́ bɛtɨk ɛbhi ndu bɛghati bho Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́-nɛ. Akʉ nɔ ndǔ áchyɛ́ mɛ bɛtaŋ ɛbhi.
\v 8 Tɛ̌ndu mbɨ́kɨ́ ghaka mbɔ yɛ̌ mmu Mandɛm achak, yi atɔŋ mɛ bɛrɨ̌ndu, áchyɛ́ mɛ bɛtɨk bɛghati bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl áfɔ́k anɛ áfù ntá Kristo. Áfɔ́k wu áya ɛnyu ɛnɛ́ mmu apu kway bɛjwimɛm ndǔ wu ankɛm achi.
\v 9 Bɛtɨk bɛchak ɛbhɛn yi áchyɛ́ mɛ chi bɛ nkʉ́ bǒ mankɛm mángɔ́ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn Mandɛm mmu ághókó mɛnyɨŋ mɛnkɛm ábhʉ́rɛ́ nyaka bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́ ndǔ mpoknkɛm anɛ áfʉɛ́rɛ́ ansɛm.
\v 10 Mandɛm akʉ nɔ bɛ nɛ́nɛ, bɛfʉɛt ntá nkwɔ Kristo, ántɔ́ŋ bɛfóŋó bɛbʉ́bɛbʉ nɛ bafɔ bhap nɔ bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛtaŋ amfay ndu nɛbhʉɛt anɛ Yesu achi Mfɔ arɛ ɛnyǔ yi ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ nɛrɨŋɨ́ndak ndǔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ yi ákʉ̀.
\v 11 Mandɛm ákʉ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ yi átɨ́ nyaka tɛ mpok yi ábhɨ́kɨ́ re fʉɛt ntá Acha ywɛsɛ Yesu Kristo.
\v 12 Ndu Mandɛm ábhárɛ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ Kristo nɛ sɛ́sɨkɨ ntɨ nɛ yi, sɛ́kwáy bɛrɔŋ ntá Mandɛm ndu bɛrɛm kɛpɨ nɛ yi, kɛbhɔŋ bɛcháy nɛ kɛmakati bɛ yi ǎghòk bhɛsɛ.
\v 13 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, nchí ghati bhe bɛ bǎkɛ́ fɛrɛ amɔ ɛ̌ti bɛsɔŋɔri ɛbhɛn mɛ̌ghɔ̀ ɛ̌ti yɛka ndu bɛkwak bhe.
\s1 Pɔ̌l ǎnɨ̀kmʉɛt ɛ̌ti nkwo Yesu abhɛn Ɛ́fɛsɔs
\p 
\v 14 Ndu Mandɛm ákʉ́ bɛyǎ mɛnyɨŋ, nchí kwɛn bɛsí Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ ndǔ mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt ɛ̌ti yɛka.
\v 15 Yi afyɛ́ nnyɛ́n ɛni ndǔ manɛrɛ́kɛt ankɛm, awu amfay nɛ fá amɨk.
\v 16 Yǐ ataŋ acha nɛ abhɔŋ bɛyǎ áfɔ́k. Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ yi ankʉ batɨ̌ yɛka antaŋ amɛm ndu bɛtaŋ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ,
\v 17 bɛ Kristo ámbák amɛm batɨ yɛka mpoknkɛm ndǔ bǎsɨ́kɨ́ ntɨ nɛ yi, nɛ bɛ mǎmbak mbɔ ɛnɔk ɛnɛ bakaŋ ɛyi áchwè amɨk sayri nɛ mbɔ ɛkɛt ɛnɛ ɛ́té sɛnɛ́ ndǔ ɛkɔŋ Mandɛm.
\v 18 Ɛnyu ɛyɔ, be nɛ bo Mandɛm báchák mankɛm bǎkwáy bɛjwimɛm bɛ Kristo akɔŋ bhɛsɛ tontó ɛnyu ɛnɛ mmu apu kway bɛyɛnti yɔ.
\v 19 Mɛ̌nɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ mǎndɨ́ŋɨ́ ɛkɔŋ ɛnɛ Kristo, yɛ̌ndu sɛ́pú kway bɛrɨŋɨ yɔ ɛnkɛm, bɛ́ mǎnkwáy bɛrɔp chi mbɔ Mandɛm ndǔ ɛpɨŋ ɛyɛka.
\p 
\v 20 Mandɛm ǎkway bɛkʉ ɛncha mɛnyɨŋ mɛnkɛm ɛbhɛn sɛ̌kwáy mɛnɨkmʉɛt bɛ yi ankʉ ndǔ bɛkwak bhɛsɛ, nɛ ɛncha ɛnyǔ ɛnɛ sɛ́kway bɛkaysi bɛ chɔŋ yi ankʉ. Ǎkʉ̀ nɔ nɛ bɛtaŋ ɛbhi ɛbhɛn bɛ́kʉ̀ bɛtɨk amɛm nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛsɛ.
\v 21 Bɛsɛ bho sɛchi ndu Nkwɔ Kristo, bo Mandɛm ábhárɛ́ nɛ Yesu Kristo, sɛ́nchíɛ Mandɛm kɛnókó. Ndǔ mkpáká bho ɛnkɛm, mpoknkɛm. Amen.
\c 4
\s1 Nkwɔ Yesu báchí mbɔ mmu amɔt
\p 
\v 1 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, mɛ Pɔ̌l mǔkɛnɔŋ ɛ̌ti Yesu Acha, nchí sɛmti bhe bɛ ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛyɛka ɛ́mbák ɛnɛ ɛ́kwáy nɛ bo abhɛn Mandɛm ábhɨ́ŋɨ́ bɛ mambak abhi.
\v 2 Bɔ́ŋ ká nɛsɛptímʉɛt nɛnkɛm. Bǎkɛ́ bhak gum gum nɛ bho. Bɔ́ŋ ká ɛkɛ́bhɛ́ntɨ. Tɔ́ŋ nɔ́kɔ́ ká batɨ ɛkɔŋ, mǎnsɔt bhɔ mbɔ ɛnyǔ bachi.
\v 3 Bɔ́ŋ ká bɛyǎ ɛkwak ndu bɛkɛm nɛchɛmɛ́mʉɛt ɛnɛn Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ ákʉ́ mǎmbɔŋ bɛfʉɛt ndǔ kpák anɛ ágwɔ̀t bhe nɛ batɨ̌ bǒ Kristo.
\v 4 Bɛsɛ mankɛm sɛchi ndu mmʉɛt amɔt, sɛbhɔŋ chi Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ amɔt. Nɛ ɛchi ɛnyu ɛ́mɔt nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ ɛnyɨŋ ɛ́mɔt kɛ ɛchi ɛnɛ sɛ́bháká ntɨ arɛ, bɛ Mandɛm abhɨŋɨ bɛsɛ bɛ sɛmbɔŋ chɔŋ yɔ.
\v 5 Acha amɔt kɛ sɛ́tòk. Bɛsɛ mankɛm sɛ́noko chi ɛnyɨŋ ɛ́mɔt. Sɛ́bhɔŋ chi nɛjwiti nɛmɔt.
\v 6 Mandɛm amɔt kɛ achi, nɛ yi achi Ɛtayɛsɛ mankɛm. Achí Mfɔ bɔ̌bhi mankɛm, áfʉ̀ɛt ntá yɛsɛ bɛkʉ bɛtɨk ɛbhi nɛ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ achi nɛ bɔ̌bhi mankɛm.
\v 7 Kɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu abhɔŋ ayi njɛnti akap kɛkúrí anɛ Kristo áchyɛ́ yi ndu bɛkʉ bɛtɨk nɛ wu.
\v 8 Ɛ̌ti yɔ kɛ̌ Ɛkáti Mandɛm ɛ́rɛ̀m bɛ, “Mpok yi ákó tɛ amfay, ásɔ́t ngɛ́mtáy bo abhɛn yi ákɛ́mɛ́ bɛ́ mankoŋo yi, akɔrɛ bɛrɨ́tí mɛnyɨŋ ntá bho.”
\v 9 Kɛ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ Ɛkáti Mandɛm ɛ́rɛ̀m bɛ, “Yi akó amfay”, ɛghati bhɛsɛ bɛ yi? Ɛyɔ ɛ́tɔ̀ŋ bhɛsɛ bɛ anáŋá asɛp nyaka ndǔ ɛtɔkɔ́ bawú.
\v 10 Nkúbhɛ́ mmu anɛ ásɛ́bhɛ́ amɨk kɛ ákó kpát afʉɛ́t nɛbu, bɛ mɛnyɨŋ mɛnkɛm mɛ́mbak mbɔ ɛnyu bɛbhɔŋɔ bɛbhak.
\v 11 Nɛ yi kɛ ákɔ́rɛ́ akap ntá bho. Ntá mbɔk, achyɛ́ akap bɛbhak bǒnto. Ntá bachak, achyɛ́ akap bɛbhak barɛmɛ́ kɛpɨ̌ntɨ. Nɛ ntá abhɛnɛfu, anɛ bɛghati bho Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́, nɛ achyɛ́ mbɔk akap bɛbhak babhabhɛri.
\v 12 Kristo ákʉ́ nɔ bɛ bo mankɛm abhɛn yi áchyɛ́ batí bɛtɨk ayɔ, mánkwak bo Mandɛm bɛ mánkwáy bɛkʉ bɛtɨk ɛbhi ɛnyu ɛnɛ mmʉɛt Kristo átaŋ andɔk nɔkɔ chi ambɨ.
\v 13 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, chɔŋ bɛsɛ mankɛm sɛndɔk ambɨ mɛnoko Mmɔ Mandɛm, nɛ ndu bɛrɨŋɨ yi ɛnyu ɛ́mɔt. Mbák sɛ́chí ɛnyu ɛyɔ, chɔŋ sɛ́ngo sɛ́nsɛnɛ, nɛ sɛ́naŋa bɛbhak mbɔ Kristo.
\v 14 Sɛ́kɛ́pɛrɛ bhák bo abhɛn bachi mbɔ mɔ́áchwi anɛ mpɛ́rɛ́nyɛn ɛ́dɛ̀p ɛ́ntɛn ɛbhé ɛ́mɔt, ɛ́ndɛp ɛntɛn ɛbhé ɛchak mpok batɔŋɔ́ nse bárwɔ̀ bhɔ nɛ nsé yap. Batɔŋɔ́ nse bhɔ bákʉ̀ bo manɛm ɛbhɨ ndu bákòŋo baraká nse anɛ bɔ́ bátɔ̀ŋ.
\v 15 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ sɛ́bhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛkʉ chi bɛkɔŋ batɨ, nɛ bɛrɛm chi mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛchi tɛtɛp ɛ̌ti Mandɛm bɛ sɛ́ngo nɔkɔ ndǔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mbi kpátɛ sɛ́ndɔp chi mbɔ Kristo mmu achi ntí ntá Nkwɔ Kristo.
\v 16 Yí kɛ áchɛ̀m bǒbhi mankɛm ndǔ nkwɔ amɔt bɛ mámbák mbɔ mmu amɔt nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ mmʉɛt nkwǎ achi nɛ maŋɔk anɛ áfáŋá byoŋómʉɛt mɛnkɛm bɛ́ mmʉɛt ambak amɔt. Nɛ ndǔ mmʉɛt nkwǎ, mpok yɛ̌ntɨkɨ nɛbhʉ́ɛ́rɛ́mʉɛt ákʉ̀ ɛbhi bɛtɨk sayri, mmʉɛt ǎgò ɛrɨrɨ. Ɛnyu ɛyɔ kɛ ɛchi nɛ bǒnkwɔ Kristo. Mpok bɔ́ bákɔ̀ŋ batɨ nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ǎkʉ̀ ɛbhi bɛtɨk sayri, bákwàk batɨ mánsɛ́nɛ́ ndǔ nɛka ɛnɛn babhɔŋɔ nɛ Yesu.
\s1 Bo abhɛn Mandɛm áchɛ́mɛ́ nɛ Kristo bábhɔŋ nɛpɛ́m nɛkɔ
\p 
\v 17 Nchí ghati yɛ bhe nɛ nchí sɛmti bhe ndǔ nnyɛ́n Acha bɛ bǎbhɨkɨ pɛrɛ bhɔŋ bɛ́bhak mbɔ bo abhɛn bápú bo Israɛl. Bɔ bákɔŋ chi bɛpɔ̌ nkaysi yap.
\v 18 Báchí amɛm ɛjuri nɛ báfap nyaka bhɔ nɛ nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛn Mandɛm áchyɛ̀, mbɔnyunɛ bachi amɨ́k nɛ́mɛ́nɛ́mɛ́ ndǔ nɛjwǐmɛm ɛnap nɛ bágwɔ́t batɨ ayap amɛm.
\v 19 Bábhɨ́kɨ́ bhɔŋ yɛ̌ mandú ntíánwɔ́p. Báchyɛ́ yɛ mmʉɛt ndǔ bɛkʉ baraká ntianwɔp anɛ mmʉɛt ɛyap ɛ́yàŋ bɔ mankʉ. Bákʉ̀ barak ɛ́pusi ankɛm, nɛ bápú rɔ bɛkʉ yɔ.
\v 20 Kɛ be, puyɛ̌ ɛnyǔ ɛyɔ kɛ bátɔ́ŋ bhe ɛ̌ti Kristo.
\v 21 Nɛ mánaŋ batɔŋ be mɛnyɨŋɨ́ tɛtɛp ɛ̌ti Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ ɛ̌ti Yesu.
\v 22 Fɛrɛ́ yɛ́ ka ɛsɨ́ mkpá ayɛka anɛ áchyɛ̀ nyaka be ɛbɛ́ptí ɛkakánɛkɔ. Bɛbɛ́ptí mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn mǎŋwaka nyaka bɛkʉ bɛ́rwɔ̀ nyaka bhe nɛ mɛ́nchɔŋti nɔkɔ batɨ̌ yɛka amɛm.
\v 23 Dɔ̌ ká Mandɛm ankʉ mǎmbak bǒ bakɔ ndǔ batɨ yɛka bɛ nkaysi ywɛka ámbák nkɔ.
\v 24 Nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmǔ ywɛka abhɔŋ bɛ́fyɛ mkpá nkɔ anɛ Mandɛm aghoko, bɛ ámbák mbɔ yímbɔŋ. Mkpá nkɔ yɔ chi ɛpɨŋ ɛkɔ ɛnɛ ɛchi chak tɛtɛp bɛsí Mandɛm, nɛ ɛchi nyáŋá tɛtɛp.
\v 25 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, dɔ̌ ká baraká nse. Bɛsɛ́ mankɛm sɛ́ndɛm nɔkɔ chi tɛtɛp nɛ batɨ, mbɔnyunɛ sɛchi mbɔ bɛpókómʉɛt nyáŋá nyáŋá ndǔ mmʉɛt amɔt.
\v 26 Mbák mmu ywɛka aběntɨ, ákɛ́ rɔ bɛběntɨ bhi mɛnto yi ndǔ bɛbʉ́, nɛ ákɛ́ bhʉɛrɛ bɛběntɨ antɨ ndǔ nywɔp nɛnkɛm.
\v 27 Kɛ́chyɛ ka Satan mbi bɛ́ ándwɔ́ mmu ankʉ bɛbʉ́.
\v 28 Mmu anɛ áchi ngɛ́p ákɛ́pɛrɛ ghɛ́p aghɛ́p. Mmu abhɔŋ bɛkʉ bɛtɨk sayri ndǔ bɛkɛm nɛpɛ́m ɛni nɛ ndǔ bɛkwak bachɛ́bhɛ́bho.
\v 29 Yɛ̌ ɛbɛ́ptí ɛyɔŋ ɛ́kɛ́ fu be anyu. Dɛm nɔ́kɔ́ ká chi mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́kwàk bo mántaŋ ndǔ mbi Mandɛm mbɔ ɛnyǔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛgo. Mmu abhɔŋ bɛrɛm chi ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ ɛ́kwak abhɛn bághòk yi.
\v 30 Nɛ bǎkɛ́ kʉ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ Mandɛm ambɔŋ kɛsɔ́ti. Mandɛm achyɛ́ bhe Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ mbɔ ɛrɨŋ ɛnɛ́ ɛ́tɔ̀ŋ bɛ bǎchi bǒbhi nɛ bɛ chɔŋ anaŋa bɛfɛrɛ bhe ndǔ kɛsɛm ɛwak ɛ́mɔt.
\v 31 Dɔ̌ ká nkaysi bɛyǎ mpap, nɛ bɛběntɨ, nɛ ɛchoko-ntɨ, nɛ bɛ́táŋá, nɛ bɛchɔŋti manyɛ́n batɨ, nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ nkaysi bɛkʉ batɨ bɛbʉ́.
\v 32 Tɔ́ŋ ká batɨ bɛrɨ, mǎngɔ bhɔ ntínso. Nɛ foŋorí nɔ́kɔ́ ká batɨ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Mandɛm áfʉɛ́rɛ́ ntá Kristo afoŋori bhe.
\c 5
\s1 Ɛpɨŋ ɛnɛ́ ɛ́kway nɛ nkwɔ́ Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Tɛ̌ndu bǎchi bɔ̌ Mandɛm nɛ yi akɔŋ be tontó, ŋɔkɔ́ yɛka ɛpɨŋ ɛyi.
\v 2 Bǎbhɔŋ bɛkɔŋ bo ndǔ nɛpɛ́m ɛnɛka nɛnkɛm nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Kristo ákɔ́ŋɔ́ bhɛsɛ nɛ áchyɛ́ nɛpɛ́m ɛni ɛ̌ti yɛsɛ. Áchyɛ́ mmʉɛt mbɔ akabhɛ́nya anɛ áchyɛ́ Mandɛm bɛyǎ maŋák.
\v 3 Bǎchi bo Mandɛm. Bǎkɛ́ bhɔŋ yɛ̌nyɨŋ bɛkʉ nɛ ɛpúsí, nɛ bɛbɛ́ptí nkaysi. Bǎkɛ́ fyɛ́ amɨ́k ndǔ mɛnyɨŋɨ́ bo bachak. Bǎkɛ rɔ mbɔŋ bɛ mántáká mɛnyɨ̌ŋ ɛbhɔ ndu nkwɔ ywɛka.
\v 4 Bǎkɛ́ rɛm yɛ̌ bɛpɔ̌-kɛpɨ nɛ bɛbhokori kɛpɨ, nɛ bǎkɛ́ kʉ bɛchoŋó ntok. Kɛ chyɛ́ nɔ́kɔ́ ká bakak ntá Mandɛm.
\v 5 Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ yɛ̌ nkoŋo baghɔrɛ́, nɛ yɛ̌ chi mmu anɛ ntɨ ɛni nɛ́pú amɛm pɛ́pɛ́p, nɛ mmu anɛ afyɛ́ amɨ́k ndǔ mɛnyɨŋ bo bachak apú bhɔŋ ákɔ́rɛ́ ndǔ nɛbhʉɛt kɛfɔ Kristo nɛ Mandɛm. Mmu anɛ afyɛ́ amɨ́k ndǔ mɛnyɨŋ bo bachak achi mbɔ mmu anɛ ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɔmandɛm bachak mbɔnyunɛ akɔŋ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ acha Mandɛm.
\v 6 Bǎkɛ́ ka yɛ bɛ mmu ánsɔ́t bɛyɔŋ ɛbhɛn bɛchi fuu andwɔ̀ bhe. Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ mɛnyǔ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ kɛ bɛ́kʉ̀ Mandɛm ambentɨ, nɛ chɔŋ antɛmsi bo abhɛn bapu ghok yi.
\v 7 Bǎkɛ́ bhak ndǔ nsoŋ amɔt nɛ mɛnyǔ bǒbhɔ.
\v 8 Bě bǎchi nyaka ndǔ ɛjuri. Nɛ̌nɛ, ɛnɛ́ Mandɛm áchɛ́mɛ́ bhe nɛ Yesu Acha, bɔ́ŋ ká ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛnɛ ɛ́kwáy nɛ bo abhɛn bachi amɛm bɛdiɛ́rɛ́.
\v 9 Bɛdiɛrɛ́ bɛ́kʉ̀ bo mǎmbɔŋ ɛrɨ́tí ɛpɨŋ, mámbak chak, nɛ mámbak bo abhɛn bachi tɛtɛp.
\v 10 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ánú bɛrɨŋɨ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́chyɛ Acha bɛyǎ maŋák.
\v 11 Bǎkɛ́ fyɛ́ mmʉɛt ndǔ bɛkʉ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bo abhɛn bachi amɛm ɛjuri bákʉ̀. Mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ bɛ́chí ndɛ́ndɛm. Bǎbhɔŋ bɛkʉ bo mandɨŋɨ kpoŋoroŋ bɛ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ bɛ́bɛp.
\v 12 Mbɔŋ bɛ́rɛm ɛ̌ti mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɔ bákʉ̀ bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́ chi ɛnyɨŋɨ́ ntíánwɔ́p.
\v 13 Mpok bɛdiɛ́rɛ́ bɛ́ghɔ̀ ndǔ ɛnyɨŋ, bɛ́tɔ̀ŋ ɛnyu yɔ ɛchi,
\v 14 mbɔnyunɛ bɛdiɛ́rɛ́ kɛ bɛ́kʉ̀ mángɔ́ ɛnyɨŋ. Ndu ɛchi nɔ kɛ bárɛ̀m bɛ,
\q1 “Mbʉɛrɛ kɛnɔ́, ŋɛmɛ́!
\q1 Fú ndǔ nɛwú,
\q1 nɛ chɔŋ bɛdiɛ́rɛ́ Kristo mɛ́ngɔ wɔ amʉɛt.”
\p 
\v 15 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ánsɔt yɛ mpok nɛ ɛkakánɛkɔ ɛyi. Bǎkɛ́ bhak mbɔ bɛchɨŋtǐ bho. Bák ká chi mbɔ barɨŋɨ́ndak.
\v 16 Kʉ ka bɛrɨ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mpok anɛ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ mbi bɛkʉ nɔ, mbɔnyunɛ bɛyǎ bo bákʉ̀ bɛbɛ́ptí mɛnyɨŋ nɛ́nɛ.
\v 17 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, bǎkɛ́ bhak bɛchɨŋtǐ bho. Nu ka bɛ́rɨ́ŋɨ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ Acha áyàŋ mǎnkʉ.
\v 18 Bǎkɛ́ bhak bakwɛnɛ́ mmɛ́m. Ɛyɔ ɛ́kʉ̀ mmu ákɛ́ kway bɛkɛm mmʉɛt, ɛ́ntwɔ yɛ yi nɛ mɛ́nɛ́mɛ́. Kɛ dɔ̌ ká Ɛfóŋó Mandɛm ambak nɛ bhe, ambɔ́ŋ bɛtaŋ ndǔ nɛpɛ́m yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka.
\v 19 Kwáy nɔ́kɔ́ ka mɛnyǔ bakwáy Nku Nsɨ́, nɛ bakwáy Mandɛm, nɛ bakwáy anɛ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ áchyɛ̀ ndu bɛ́fyɛ́ batɨ ntɨ. Kwáy nɔ́kɔ́ ka bakway ndu bɛbɨti Acha nɛ batɨ yɛka ankɛm.
\v 20 Kaká ká Ɛtayɛsɛ Mandɛm mpoknkɛm ɛ̌ti yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ ndǔ nnyɛ́n Yesu Kristo Acha.
\s1 Ɛnyǔ baghɔrɛ́ nɛ manɛ́m abhap bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛ́bhak
\p 
\v 21 Sɛptí nɔ́kɔ́ ka mmʉɛt ntá batɨ. Ɛpɨŋ ɛyɔ ɛ́mfú ndǔ kɛnókó ɛkɛn bǎchyɛ̀ Kristo.
\v 22 Baghɔrɛ́ nɛbhay, sɛptí nɔ́kɔ́ ká mmʉɛt ntá manɛ́m abhɛka mbɔ ɛnyǔ bǎsɛpti mmʉɛt ntá Acha.
\v 23 Nnɛ́m achi mǔnti ntá ngɔrɛ́ ywi mbɔ ɛnyǔ Kristo achi mǔnti ntá bǒnkwɔ. Bǒnkwɔ chi mmʉɛt yi nɛ yímbɔŋ kɛ ápɛ̀mɛ bhɔ.
\v 24 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ngɔrɛ́ abhɔŋ yɛ bɛsɛpti mmʉɛt ntá nnɛ́m aywi ndǔ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ, mbɔ ɛnyǔ bǒnkwɔ básɛ̀pti mmʉɛt ntá Kristo.
\p 
\v 25 Bě manɛ́m, yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka abhɔŋ bɛkɔŋ ngɔrɛ́ ywi nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Kristo ákɔ́ŋ bǒnkwɔ nɛ agú ɛ̌ti yap.
\v 26 Agú bɛ́kʉ bɔ mámbák pɛ́pɛ́p bɛsí Mandɛm ndu ásó bhɔ nɛ manyiɛp nɛ Ɛyɔŋ Mandɛm.
\v 27 Kristo akʉ nɔ́ bɛ ankway bɛkʉ nkwɔ Kristo mantwɔ ntá yi nɛ bɛyǎ bɛrɨ, kɛbhɔ́ŋ yɛ̌nyɨŋ ɛnɛ ɛ́kʉ̀ Mandɛm nɛ yɛ̌ chi bo mánji bhɔ.
\v 28 Ɛnyu ɛyɔ nkwɔ kɛ ɛchi bɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ nnɛ́m abhɔŋ bɛkɔŋ ngɔrɛ́ ywi mbɔ mmʉɛt yi. Mmu anɛ ákɔ̀ŋ ngɔrɛ́ ywi ǎkɔ̀ŋ chi mmʉɛt yi.
\v 29 Mmǔ anɛ ápábhɛ́ mmʉɛt yi apú. Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu áyɨ̀ŋɨ mmʉɛt yi sayri ankɛ́m yɔ ɛrɨrɨ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Kristo áyɨ̀ŋɨ bǒnkwɔ,
\v 30 nɛ bɛsɛ mankɛm sɛchi bɛpókómʉɛt ɛbhi.
\v 31 Ɛkáti Mandɛm ɛ́rɛ̀m bɛ,
\q1 “Mbakanɛm abhɔŋ bɛrɔ máyi nɛ ɛtayi
\q1 anchɛm mmʉɛt nɛ ngɔrɛ́ ywi,
\q1 bɔ bati apay mándɔp mmǔ amɔt.”
\p 
\v 32 Bɛyɔŋ ɛbhɛn bɛ́rɛ̀m ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ ɛchi bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́. Ndɨ́ŋɨ́ bɛ bɛ́rɛ̀m chi ɛnyǔ Kristo achi nɛ Nkwɔ Kristo.
\v 33 Kɛ ɛ́chí ɛnyu ɛyɔ nɛ bhe nkwɔ. Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu abhɔŋ bɛkɔŋ ngɔrɛ́ ywi mbɔnyu ákɔ́ŋɔ́ mmʉɛt ɛyi yímbɔŋ, nɛ yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ngɔrɛ́ abhɔŋ bɛchyɛ nnɛ́m ywi kɛnókó.
\c 6
\s1 Ɛnyǔ bɔ́ bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛbhak nɛ bɔmáyap nɛ bachi bhap
\p 
\v 1 Bɔ, yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka abhɔŋ bɛghok máyi nɛ ɛtayi, mbɔnyunɛ bǎchi bakoŋo Acha nɛ ɛchi chak bɛkʉ nɔ.
\v 2 “Nokó ka manɔ nɛ bachi bhɛka.” Ɛnɛ, chí ɛbhé mbɨ ɛnɛ́ Mandɛm afyɛ́ bariɛp amɛn abhak nɛ mmu anɛ ábhʉ̀rɛ yɔ.
\v 3 Bariɛp amɔ achi bɛ, “Mmǔ anɛ ábhʉ̀ɛrɛ ɛbhé ɛnɛ, yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ ɛbhak sayri nɛ yi, nɛ ǎbhɔŋ ɛrɔri nɛpɛ́m fá amɨk.”
\p 
\v 4 Bě bachǐbhɔ, bǎkɛ́ bhɔŋ ɛpɨŋ bɛkʉ batɨ ambe bɔ̌ bhɛka. Ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛkʉ chi mɛ́nyúrɛ nɛ bɛtɔŋ bhɔ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Acha áyàŋ.
\s1 Ɛnyǔ basɛm nɛ bachi bhap bábhɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛbhak
\p 
\v 5 Basɛm, yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka abhɔŋ bɛ́ghok mmu anɛ ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ yi fá amɨk sayri. Chiɛ́ nɔ́kɔ́ ka bhɔ kɛnókó nɛ bɛchǎy nɛ nɛwɛrɛ́mʉɛt nɛ mǎnkʉ nɔ́kɔ́ bɛtɨk ɛbhɛka nɛ ntɨ nɛmɔt nkúbhɛ́ mbɔ ɛnyǔ bághòk Kristo.
\v 6 Bǎkɛ́ ghok bhɔ chi ndiɛrɛ bɛsí bhap nɛ ndǔ bɛkʉ bɔ mambɔŋ maŋák. Kɛ kʉ ka ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ Mandɛm áyàŋ mǎnkʉ nɛ ntɨ nɛnkɛm mbɔ basɛm Kristo.
\v 7 Kʉ nɔ́kɔ́ ka bɛtɨk nɛ maŋák mbɔ bɛ bǎtòk chi Acha, puyɛ̌ nkwǎ.
\v 8 Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ yi ǎkap yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu bɛkoŋo bɛrɨ ɛbhɛn yi ákʉ́, yɛ̌ achi nsɛm, yɛ apu.
\p 
\v 9 Bě nkwɔ bho bǎbhɔ́ŋɔ́ basɛm, kɛ́m ká bhɔ sayri. Bǎkɛ́ pá bɛchyɛ bhɔ ntɛmsi. Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ Ɛta mmu achi amfay kɛ ábhɔ́ŋɔ́ be nɛ bhɔ, nɛ yi apú tɔŋ kɛ́rɨ́ŋámík.
\s1 Mɛnyɨŋɨ́ nɛnu ɛbhɛn bo Mandɛm
\p 
\v 10 Ɛnyɨŋɨ́ ngwɛnti ɛnɛ nchí ghati bhe chi ɛnɛ: Kɛ́m ká nɛbhárɛ́mʉɛt ɛnɛka nɛ Acha bɛ mǎntáŋ nɛ bɛtaŋ ɛbhi ɛbhɛn bɛyǎ bɛcha.
\v 11 Kɛ́m ká mɛnyɨŋɨ́ nɛnu mɛnkɛm ɛbhɛn Mandɛm áchyɛ̀, bɛ́ mǎnkwáy mɛnu nɛ Satan, mǎnte kpirí mpok yi áyàŋ bɛrwɔ bhe.
\v 12 Dɨŋɨ́ ká bɛ sɛ́pú nu chi nɛ bakwǎŋwaŋ. Sɛ́nù chi nɛ bɛbɛ́ptí bɛfóŋó, nɛ bafɔ bhap, nɛ mɛnyǔ bɛtaŋ bɛchak. Sɛ́nù nkwɔ nɛ bɛfóŋó ɛbhɛn bɛbhɔŋɔ bɛtaŋ ndǔ mmɨk ɛjuri nɛ, nɛ sɛ́nù nɛ ngɛ́mtáy bɛfóŋó bɛbʉ́bɛbʉ ɛbhɛn bɛbhɔŋɔ bɛtaŋ amfay ndǔ mbʉ́ɛ́p.
\v 13 Yɛ̌ntɨkɨ mmu ywɛka ánsɔt yɛ mɛnyɨŋɨ́ nɛnu mɛnkɛm ɛbhɛn Mandɛm áchyɛ̀, bɛ mpok ɛsɔŋɔri ántwɔ́, mǎnu tɛ ndǔ ngwɛnti, nɛ mǎndɔk ambɨ bɛte kpirí.
\v 14 Ndu ɛchi nɔ, dɔ́k ká ambɨ bɛte kpɨrí. Tɛtɛp anɛ bǎrɨ́ŋɨ́ ámbák mbɔ mgbat anɛ ákɛ̀m mɛnyɨŋí nɛnu ɛbhɛka. Kʉ nɔ́kɔ́ ká chi ndiɛrɛ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn bɛchi chak mbɔnyunɛ mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɔ bɛchi mbɔ nkú bɛsé anɛ ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu afyɛ́ ndu bɛkuti mbeápak ɛyi.
\v 15 Ghatí nɔ́kɔ́ ka bo Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ ákʉ̀ bɔ mambɔŋ kpák bɛsí Mandɛm. Ndǔ bǎkʉ̀ nɔ, ɛbhak mbɔ mpok ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu afyɛ́ bɛtaŋtí nkwɔbhɛ́nya bɛ́ ákɛ́ kwɛn amɨk mpok ájɛ̀t ntyɛt.
\v 16 Ɛnyɨŋ ɛ́chák chi bɛ mǎndɔ́k ambɨ bɛbhɔŋ nɛka nɛ Kristo, bɛ nɛ́mbák ɛkuti ɛyɛka mbɔ ɛnɛ ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu ákɛ̀m awɔ́ bɛ anchyɛt bakɔŋ anɛ ádù nɛ ngó anɛ́ mbʉ́mbʉ átò.
\v 17 Bǎrɨŋɨ bɛ Mandɛm apɛ́mɛ́ bhe. Bɛrɨŋɨ nɔ ǎbhák ndǔ nkaysi ayɛka mbɔ kɛndɛ́n anɛ ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu ákùti ntí ywi nɛ yɔ. Sɔt ka nkwɔ́ Ɛyɔŋ Mandɛm ɛnɛ́ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ áchyɛ́ bhe mbɔ akparɛnja nsɛm ɛpay anɛ ntɛmɛ́ nɛnu.
\v 18 Nɨk nɔ́kɔ́ ká mmʉɛt mpoknkɛm nɛ ɛ̌ti yɛ̌ntɨkɨ ɛnyɨŋ mbɔ ɛnyǔ Ɛfóŋó Bɛdyɛrɛ áyà bhe mbi. Bǎk ká pě. Kɛ́m nɔ́kɔ́ ká ɛkɨ́kɨ́ ndǔ nɛnɨkɨ́mʉɛt ɛ̌ti bǒ Mandɛm mankɛm bɛ yi ankwak bhɔ.
\v 19 Nɨk nɔ́kɔ́ ká mmʉɛt ɛ̌ti ya nkwɔ bɛ Mandɛm anchyɛ mɛ ɛnyɨŋ ɛnɛ mbɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛghati bo ɛ̌ti Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ anɛ achi nyaka bhɛ́sɛ́ bhɛ́sɛ́ nkɛbhɔŋ bɛcháy.
\v 20 Ɛ̌ti Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ kɛ̌ Kristo ásɔ́rɛ́ mɛ, akʉ mɛ nté ndǔ ntí ywi, nɛ nchí mǔkɛnɔŋ nɛ́nɛ. Nɨk nɔ́kɔ́ ká mmʉɛt bɛ Mandɛm anchyɛ mɛ nɛtaŋántɨ bɛ ngátí nɔkɔ bho Mbok Ndɨ́ndɨ́ mbɔnyu mbɔ́ŋɔ́ bɛkʉ.
\s1 Pɔ̌l ǎnɨ̀kmʉɛt bɛ Mandɛm anjɛt bakoŋo Yesu
\p 
\v 21 Chɔŋ Tíkíkɔs antwɔ́ awu angati bhe ndǔ mɛnyɨŋ bɛchi fá nɛ mɛ nɛ ɛ̌ti mɛnyɨŋ ɛbhɛn mɛ́kʉ̀. Achi manɔ ywɛsɛ anɛ sɛ́kɔ́ŋɔ́. Achi nkʉbɛtɨk anɛ Acha nɛ yí achi mmu anɛ abhʉrɛ bariɛp ami.
\v 22 Ɛ̌ti yɔ, kɛ nchí to yi ntá yɛka bɛ ankʉ mǎndɨŋɨ ɛnyu bɛsɛ sɛchi, nɛ bɛ́ ámfyɛ́ bhe ntɨ.
\v 23 Mandɛm Ɛtayɛsɛ nɛ Yesu Kristo Acha mánchyɛ́ běka bǒnkwɔ kpák, mánkwak be bɛ mǎnkɔŋ batɨ, nɛ bɛ mǎndɔ́k ambɨ bɛbhɔŋ nɛka nɛ Yesu Kristo.
\v 24 Nchí nɨkmʉɛt bɛ Mandɛm ántɔ́ŋ bɛrɨ̌ndu ɛbhi ntá bǒ mankɛm abhɛn bákɔ́ŋɔ́ Yesu Kristo Acha nɛ ɛkɔŋ ɛnɛ ɛpu gu manyiɛp.
